  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Favorites.OnFavoritesListener
    listens to Favorites operations.
    HttpPost.HttpPostListener
    interface to implement the callbacks of the http operation of HttpPost
    ImageDownloader.OnImageDownloaderListener
    interface to implement the callbacks of the operation of ImageDownloader
    MovieHelper.OnFetchListener
    listens to MovieHelper operations.
    Search.OnSearchListener
    listener for Search operations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Favorites
    provides functions to add/remove movie to favorite list as well as storing and restoring the list locally.
    HttpPost
    helper class to handle the http posts.
    ImageDownloader
    helper to download image from the server and store it.
    MovieHelper
    provides functions for a movie to fetch poster , rating and release.
    Search
    provides the functions to search a movie from Omdb api.
